metadata.name: Spax #1
metadata.description: Spax is a collectible NFT Avatar that you can use anywhere in the metaverse and in your online social life. Spax is a community-based collection project featuring artworks by Safa Paksu. In this collection consisting of 5000 men and 5000 women, each avatar has its own unique and equal trait in terms of value.
